Greek /ɡriːk/

(Greeks) 

1. ADJ Greek means belonging or relating to Greece. 希腊的 

2. N-COUNT A Greek is a person who comes from Greece. 希腊人 

3. N-UNCOUNT Greek is the language used in Greece. 希腊语 

例： I had to learn Greek. 我只好学希腊语。 

4. N-UNCOUNT Greek or Ancient Greek was the language used in Greece in ancient times. 古希腊语

